        "description": "Full-bleed organic foliage in #193c35, #7e813c, #e5ba2b, #ec4f22, #c6d7d0. Flat vector style with no gradients. Abstract shapes that bleed off page edges. No border, no container — the illustration IS the container."
      },
      {
